{"tid":379433,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"[音樂研究] 求 北角協同中學 & 馬錦明慈善基金馬陳端喜紀念中學 校歌","createTime":"2017-08-29T10:33:29.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-29T13:29:03.000Z","uid":48088,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"1aa9d9befd44bb623ad30f8f95a44e9ea2d1e66f","tid":379433,"uid":48088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T10:33:29.000Z","msg":"[代朋友 post]<br />\n<br />\n筆者為音樂、歷史及語言學學者，現正進行關於香港路德會學校校歌的研究，主力分析樂曲結構及歌詞意境，並希望能將香港路德會學校的校歌介紹予海外讀者；<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">現請求下列學校校歌歌譜與歌詞</span></strong>，以進行研究:<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>北角協同中學<br />\n馬錦明慈善基金馬陳端喜紀念中學</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n校歌資料將於本年九月瑞典Uppsala大學Lutheran Music Culture Conference 2017 先行發表，與會者包括一百多位來自三十多國路德會音樂研究學者。<br />\n<br />\n感謝協助，感激在心中！"},{"pid":"6bf2dce158fe8912f7a4f8253cfcc0fda0ee0e51","tid":379433,"uid":48088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T13:16:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b04bfc4aa669c7065884ae61ae3f2627afd6261","tid":379433,"uid":23416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T13:29:03.000Z","msg":"年青人 沾沐主恩 肩負人類社會責任"}]}